'''夏莎莉·馬賀拉'''（[[印度語|印度語]]：हर्षाली मल्होत्रा，{{lang-en|Harshaali Malhotra}}，{{bd|2008年|6月3日|catIdx=M}}）是[[印度|印度]]女童星。2015年，她和[[寶萊塢|寶萊塢]]男影星[[薩爾曼·汗|薩爾曼·汗]]（Salman Khan）及女星[[卡琳娜·卡浦爾|卡琳娜·卡浦爾]]（Kareena Kapoor）合作並在拍攝了她首套電影《[[小萝莉的猴神大叔|小萝莉的猴神大叔]]》 ，該電影票房大賣，是印度史上最賣座的寶萊塢電影的名單上排名第二位。<ref>[http://www.ibtimes.co.in/bajrangi-bhaijaan-17-day-box-office-collection-salman-starrer-dethrones-aamirs-dhoom-3-641421 "'Bajrangi Bhaijaan' 17-Day Box Office Collection: Salman Starrer Dethrones Aamir's 'Dhoom 3'; Becomes second Highest Bollywood Grosser of All Time"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/bajrangi-bhaijaan-17-day-box-office-collection-salman-starrer-dethrones-aamirs-dhoom-3-641421 |date=20151005141909 }}. International Business Times, India Edition. 3 August 2015.</ref>馬賀拉在電影中扮演一名不會說話並在印度和母親失散的巴基斯坦女孩Shahida/Munni也使她知名度提升。馬賀拉的演出備受讚賞。<ref>[http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/not-salman-khan-harshali-malhotra-is-real-star-of-bajrangi-bhaijaan-kareena-kapoor/ "Not Salman Khan, Harshali Malhotra is the real star of ‘Bajrangi Bhaijaan’: Kareena Kapoor - See more at: http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/not-salman-khan-harshali-malhotra-is-real-star-of-bajrangi-bhaijaan-kareena-kapoor/#sthash.cBsQr51M.dpuf"] {{Wayback|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/not-salman-khan-harshali-malhotra-is-real-star-of-bajrangi-bhaijaan-kareena-kapoor/ |date=20150929023436 }} The Indian Express, 20 June 2015.</ref>

